{"tid":1748454,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"毛ee、GPhone、鄺神出左咁多力，仲話割泛民？","createTime":"2019-11-23T16:31:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T03:44:48.000Z","uid":232261,"like":102,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"06ed9c824e486030a0076d8e52212a7e54bd8f19","tid":1748454,"uid":232261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T16:31:57.000Z","msg":"三毛唔好再分化再屌泛民啦！<br />\n<br />\n呢幾個月，毛ee、GPhone國際線出左幾多力。鄺仔走遍全港咁多區升呢做埋鄺神，連登仔一定會記得<br />\n<br />\n唔好再話投白票。無人想對住個日日屌甲由，日日嗌止暴制亂既廢老區議員4年<br />\n<br />\n食飯都分黃藍店，投票更加要分黃藍。識投一定投建制對家！用選票懲罰無恥藍絲廢老！<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！"},{"pid":"9ddd8920c1bd1db00fae982d956eeb1e4a5b5e00","tid":1748454,"uid":232261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T16:32:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dc327dc60d6540b9563714c7409008edd801aca7","tid":1748454,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T16:33:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f42f08dc70db49aed6c9a74ac0d94eb64f646a1","tid":1748454,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T16:34:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8a4754cd6fcbf5ad50f4bb4e380c5bba7878f606","tid":1748454,"uid":157938,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T16:34:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n投票踢走保皇黨 就係咁簡單"},{"pid":"91eb4927e9f70b2be43369e9a33387ea151bdf74","tid":1748454,"uid":327462,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T16:34:45.000Z","msg":"仲有許智峯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d47c3ceaa3fcf8df44b1c8b3be4e95442317203c","tid":1748454,"uid":159928,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T16:34:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e30839ee1943839a2e88d1caeb50562d1aca7f69","tid":1748454,"uid":265935,"like":0,"disli